            <div class="container"><section class="hero w-100"><div class="hero-image gradient" style="background:url('images/imm-homepage-1440x400.jpg') no-repeat center / cover;"><div class="max-w-1120 hero-text" id="slick-slide00"><h1>Advancing treatment of immune-regulated diseases.</h1></div></div></section></div><section class="container"><div class="section-top"><h3>Our Mission</h3></div><div class="max-w-980"><p>The mission of the Center for Human Immunobiology at Northwestern University Feinberg School of Medicine is to discover and translate innovative science into cures for immune-regulated diseases.&#160;</p>
<p class="text-center"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="about/index.html">About Us</a> <a class="btn btn-primary" href="members/index.html">Become a Member</a></p></div></section><section class="container"><div class="section-top"><h3>Our Work</h3></div><div class="container feature-two-col max-w-1120"><div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="feature-box col-md-6"><div class="feature-img "><img alt="" src="images/microscope-550x310.jpg"/></div><div class="feature-copy"><h4>Research </h4>Center members have access to our scientific resources, such as immunology core facilities.</div><a class="btn btn-primary w-100" href="research/index.html">Browse Research Initiatives</a></div><div class="feature-box col-md-6"><div class="feature-img "><img alt="" src="images/researcher-550x310.jpg"/></div><div class="feature-copy"><h4>Education</h4>We support a variety of educational programs, including postdoctoral training in immunology.</div><a class="btn btn-primary w-100" href="education/index.html">See Education Opportunities</a></div></div></div></section>
